n傀儡在明<br />\n共諜在暗<br />\n<br />\n傀儡係額頭印撚住&quot;唔係自己人&quot;<br />\n共諜係額頭印撚住&quot;自己人&quot;<br />\n<br />\n正如<br />\n熱青城光明正大係FACEBOOK奶施永青等大孖沙或政協袋底就係大孖沙或政協傀儡<br />\n泛民入面某幾個唔聲唔聲為大孖沙或政協通過某D發大財議案係大孖沙或政協間諜"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-08T03:39:58.000Z","msg":"你地都可以幫佢地兜話係想CONNECT班淺藍屍大孖沙同政協既<br />\n不過一個就光明正大咁CONNECT, 一個就靜靜雞地CONNECT咁囉<br />\n泛民叫你地唔好無差別裝修咪就係暗地裡CONNECT班淺藍大孖沙囉<br />\n陳雲同黃洋達最近果2個FB POST咪就係光明正大咁奶深藍同淺藍屍大孖沙袋底囉屌"},{"pid":"633f21d88a3546b4c5e17b558c3b23acc14e3de1","tid":1773913,"uid":253320,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-08T03:46:29.000Z","msg":"成篇文太多撚字好難睇明"},{"pid":"07f41e8bfdc103fa6a725f06472ab008b52de60b","tid":1773913,"uid":271199,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-08T03:49:17.000Z","msg":"除左個班堅實班底on9信徒，應該無人會信佢地 / 無新血加入"},{"pid":"401c2a49834ffe361a8b136800924a43b2100e3d","tid":1773913,"uid":155784,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-08T03:58:09.000Z","msg":"唔奇，十一哥同屈穎妍以前都係民主派<br />\n十一哥衰雪廠街攪U16，屈穎妍有次上大陸宣揚民主，俾公安捉左之後返來變左文妓<br />\n<br />\n中共對捉痛腳好有經驗<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a099191335781b27ecf15b634ac949aa19ec804b","tid":1773913,"uid":20867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-08T04:02:43.000Z","msg":"關青年新政咩事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee09241afa8c20f80b7fb3d585821c8d7688b7ce","tid":1773913,"uid":58089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-08T04:06:35.000Z","msg":"講黎無意思 拉"},{"pid":"c8468369edd0b16d084a04a23b3c119bc7e025cd","tid":1773913,"uid":31637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a099191335781b27ecf15b634ac949aa19ec804b","tid":1773913,"uid":20867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-08T04:02:43.000Z","msg":"關青年新政咩事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" clas